08/12/2002
SARAJEVO, Bosnia and Herzegovina (BiH) -- The Office of the High Representative (OHR) and the EU's Customs and Financial Assistance Office announced Friday (6 December) that they would join forces in fighting tax evasion and money laundering in BiH. 
High Representative Paddy Ashdown told reporters that the OHR would team up with the Independent Judicial Commission, responsible for judicial reforms in BiH, to examine the conditions that allow illegal money transfers to be made. 
(OHR website, PBS - 06/12/02)
